# 💼 Nelian Achieng' Portfolio Website

Welcome to my personal developer portfolio! This is a **fully responsive and interactive** website built using **HTML**, **CSS**, and **JavaScript**, designed to showcase my skills, interests, projects, education, and contact information with modern animations and engaging user interactions.

## 🌟 Live Demo

👉 [Visit the Live Site](https://illustrious-beignet-e768e7.netlify.app/)

---

## 📌 Features

### 🎨 **Visual & Animations**
- ✨ Smooth scrolling with scroll-triggered animations
- 📊 Real-time scroll progress bar at the top
- 🎯 Active navigation highlighting based on scroll position
- 💫 Floating particle effects in hero section
- ⌨️ Typing effect animation for subtitle
- 🎭 Parallax scrolling effect on hero section
- 🖱️ Interactive cursor trail effect (desktop only)
- 🌈 Shimmer effect on profile image

### 🔧 **Interactive Features**
- 📱 Fully functional mobile hamburger menu
- ⬆️ Back-to-top button with smooth scroll
- 📈 Animated skill progress bars
- 🎴 Hover effects on project and skill cards
- 📧 Contact form with toast notifications
- 🔄 3D rotation effects on skill icons
- 💬 Success messages after form submission

### 🎮 **Special Features**
- 🕹️ Easter egg with Konami Code (↑↑↓↓←→←→BA)
- 💻 Developer greeting in browser console
- 🎨 Gradient text effects throughout
- 🌟 Card hover transformations and shadows

### ♿ **Accessibility & Performance**
- 📱 Fully responsive design for all devices
- ⚡ Lazy loading for optimized performance
- ⌨️ Enhanced focus states for keyboard navigation
- 🎯 Semantic HTML structure
- 🔍 SEO-friendly markup

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

- **HTML5** - Semantic markup and structure
- **CSS3** - Advanced styling with:
  - Flexbox & Grid layouts
  - CSS Variables for theming
  - Keyframe animations
  - Transitions and transforms
  - Backdrop filters
  - Gradient effects
- **JavaScript (ES6+)** - Interactive features:
  - DOM manipulation
  - Intersection Observer API
  - Event listeners
  - Smooth scrolling
  - Dynamic content generation
  - Form handling
- **SVG** - Background grain effect
- **Responsive Design** - Mobile-first approach

